last_episode_to_air.name: Okay Fine, It's a Hurricane
last_episode_to_air.overview: Everyone heads to Pemberton's to weather out the hurricane.

name: How I Met Your Father
overview: In the near future, Sophie tells her son the story of how she met his father: a story that catapults us back to the year 2021 where Sophie and her close-knit group of friends are in the midst of figuring out who they are, what they want out of life, and how to fall in love in the age of dating apps and limitless options.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: After a slew of let-down Tinder dates, Sophie meets the seemingly perfect guy. Meanwhile, her roommate, Valentina, returns home from London Fashion Week with a sexy souvenir. An Uber-related phone mishap leads them to an eclectic new group of friends.

episodes.name: FOMO
episodes.overview: Determined to try and live in the moment, Sophie and the gang head to an exclusive new club for a wild night out. Valentina has doubts about her relationship with Charlie. Sid pushes Jesse to be open to love. Ellen tries her luck with women at the club.

episodes.name: The Fixer
episodes.overview: While helping Jesse take photos for his new Tinder profile, Sophie feels sparks with someone unexpected. Valentina helps Sid with his long distance relationship. Ellen and Charlie go apartment hunting.

episodes.name: Dirrty Thirty
episodes.overview: Sophie discovers that hosting her thirtieth birthday party is almost as stressful as turning thirty. Jesse and Ellen struggle to relate as siblings. Val and Charlie spice things up. Sid shows off a new piece of bling.

episodes.name: The Good Mom
episodes.overview: An unexpected visit from Sophie's mom heightens Val's concern for her friend. Charlie helps Jesse and Sid face past traumas. A culinary quest leads Ellen to someone new.

episodes.name: Stacey
episodes.overview: Sophie feels haunted by her boyfriend's ex. Sid and Hannah hash out an old argument. Charlie and Ellen host a dinner party.

episodes.name: Rivka Rebel
episodes.overview: Valentina helps Sophie with an unexpected career opportunity. Jesse and Sid struggle with procrastination. Charlie seeks out a nasty Yelp reviewer.

episodes.name: The Perfect Shot
episodes.overview: Sophie and Jesse navigate a day in the life of an artist. Valentina retaliates against her boss. Sid and Ellen deal with an unexpected visitor.

episodes.name: Jay Street
episodes.overview: A parental wrench is thrown into Sophie’s plan for the day. Jesse deals with the aftermath of a truth bomb. Charlie tries to get the gang excited about soccer.

episodes.name: Timing is Everything
episodes.overview: Sophie gets romantic advice from someone who's been through it all. Valentina and Charlie face a tough crossroads. Jesse makes a choice.

episodes.name: Cool and Chill
episodes.overview: After Sophie’s gallery show and Ian’s arrival, Sid and Hannah host an impromptu wedding reception at Pemberton’s. Jesse grapples with his decisions and confides in Ellen about Meredith.

episodes.name: Midwife Crisis
episodes.overview: As she waits for the gallery to call, Sophie lands a gig she lied to get and enlists Val to help. Jesse forces Sid and Meredith to work out their differences.

episodes.name: The Reset Button
episodes.overview: After selling her portrait, Sophie recruits Jesse to help her impress the buyers. Val and Ellen go on a double date. Charlie forces a reluctant Sid and Hannah into a double date in reaction to Val.

episodes.name: Pathetic Deirdre
episodes.overview: Sophie and Val question where they are in their careers and reach out to an old friend. Jesse and Meredith make a tour announcement video.

episodes.name: Ride or Die
episodes.overview: Sophie and Val have conflicting feelings about brunch with Val’s parents. The gang attends Jesse’s Long Island show.

episodes.name: Universal Therapy
episodes.overview: Sophie encounters an obstacle with a new beau. Ellen uses her new job insurance to see a therapist. Jesse gives Valentina a hand at work while Sid and Charlie try to sell terrible wine.

episodes.name: A Terrible, Horrible, No Good, Very Bad Valentine's Day
episodes.overview: The gang recounts their worst Valentine's Day experiences in order to cheer up Ellen.

episodes.name: Rewardishment
episodes.overview: Jesse and Sid introduce the gang to an old college ritual. They all spend the next 48 hours attempting to complete various tasks in order to achieve a group “rewardishment.”

episodes.name: The Welcome Protocol
episodes.overview: Val brings Sophie to a work event so they can party all night with the rich and famous. Jesse wants to introduce the friends to a new girl he’s seeing, forcing them to spring into action and invoke the “Welcome Protocol”.

episodes.name: I'm His Swish
episodes.overview: Sophie dates an older man, which encourages Jesse, Sid, and Charlie to take better care of themselves. Sophie and Val battle over who gets the apartment for date night.

episodes.name: Daddy
episodes.overview: Sophie goes to Robert's country house for the weekend. The gang celebrates Lost & Found Box Day at Pemberton's.

episodes.name: Not a Mamma Mia
episodes.overview: Sophie recruits the gang to help track down her father.

episodes.name: Family Business
episodes.overview: Sophie and her dad run a business out of Pemberton's. Charlie and Jesse meet women they like. Val and Ellen treat themselves to a fancy open house.

episodes.name: Disengagement Party
episodes.overview: Sophie pulls in the big guns to help her get Val out of her engagement. Sid and Hannah argue about where they'll live. Jesse helps Charlie and Ellen through a roommate faux pas.

episodes.name: Working Girls
episodes.overview: Sophie and Ellen get assigned to a work project together. Sid surprises Hannah in LA. Charlie and Val try to make the most of their time with Jesse after he gets a bad psychic reading.

episodes.name: The Jersey Connection
episodes.overview: Ellen suspects something is up with Rachel. She and Sid do a stakeout. Sophie tracks an upset Jesse down after he wasn't invited to a coworker's birthday party.

episodes.name: Out of Sync
episodes.overview: The gang go a day without their cell phones, forced to face the world without help from the internet.

episodes.name: Parent Trap
episodes.overview: Sophie tries to Parent Trap her parents. Sid and Ellen try their own master plan to nudge Jesse and Charlie into being roommates with each other.

episodes.name: Shady Parker
episodes.overview: Jesse tricks the gang into helping him pack his stuff in the apartment.

episodes.name: Okay Fine, It's a Hurricane
episodes.overview: Everyone heads to Pemberton's to weather out the hurricane.
